Package: glyread
Title: Read and process glycomics and glycoproteomics data
Version: 0.3.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Bin", "Fu", , "23110220018@m.fudan.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8567-2997"))
Description: This package reads and processes quantification results from
    common glycomics and glycoproteomics software, such as Byonic, StrucGP,
    or pGlyco, and converts them into a `glyexp_experiment` object 
    (from the [glyexp](https://github.com/glycoverse/glyexp) package)
    for further analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
